## 🛠️ 自動化工具

### 日誌管理腳本
```powershell
# debug-manager.ps1
function New-DebugEntry {
    param(
        [string]$Category,      # ai_assistant, editor, websocket等
        [string]$Title,         # 問題標題
        [string]$Priority,      # P0, P1, P2, P3
        [string]$Description    # 問題描述
    )
    
    $debugFile = ".cursor/debug/${Category}_debug.mdc"
    $issueNumber = Get-NextIssueNumber $debugFile
    $date = Get-Date -Format "yyyy-MM-dd"
    
    $entry = @"

## 🐛 問題 #$issueNumber - $Title - $date

### 📊 問題分類
- **優先級**: $Priority
- **影響範圍**: [待補充]
- **觸發環境**: [待補充]

### 🔍 問題現象
$Description

### 🔧 根本原因分析
[待分析]

### ✅ 解決方案
[待設計]

### 🧪 測試驗證
[待測試]

### 📈 預防措施
[待建立]

### 🔗 相關連結
- **規則檔案**: `.cursor/rules/${Category}_rules.mdc`

**狀態**: 🔄 分析中
"@

    Add-Content $debugFile $entry
    Write-Host "✅ Debug條目已創建: $debugFile #$issueNumber" -ForegroundColor Green
}

function Update-DebugStatus {
    param(
        [string]$Category,
        [int]$IssueNumber,
        [string]$Status        # ✅ 已修復, ⏳ 進行中, 🔄 重現中
    )
    
    $debugFile = ".cursor/debug/${Category}_debug.mdc"
    $content = Get-Content $debugFile
    $updatedContent = $content -replace "## 🐛 問題 #$IssueNumber.*狀態**: .*", "狀態**: $Status"
    $updatedContent | Set-Content $debugFile
    
    Write-Host "✅ 問題 #$IssueNumber 狀態已更新為: $Status" -ForegroundColor Green
}
```

### 統計報告生成
```powershell
function Generate-DebugReport {
    Write-Host "📊 生成Debug統計報告..."
    
    $debugFiles = Get-ChildItem ".cursor/debug/*_debug.mdc"
    $totalIssues = 0
    $resolvedIssues = 0
    
    foreach ($file in $debugFiles) {
        $content = Get-Content $file.FullName
        $issues = $content | Select-String "## 🐛 問題 #"
        $resolved = $content | Select-String "狀態\*\*: ✅ 已修復"
        
        $totalIssues += $issues.Count
        $resolvedIssues += $resolved.Count
        
        Write-Host "📁 $($file.BaseName): $($issues.Count) 問題, $($resolved.Count) 已修復"
    }
    
    $resolveRate = if ($totalIssues -gt 0) { ($resolvedIssues / $totalIssues * 100).ToString("F1") } else { "0" }
    
    Write-Host "📈 總體統計:"
    Write-Host "  - 總問題數: $totalIssues"
    Write-Host "  - 已修復: $resolvedIssues"
    Write-Host "  - 修復率: $resolveRate%"
    Write-Host "  - 活躍問題: $($totalIssues - $resolvedIssues)"
}
```

